snippet.title: Tuesday, February 11, 2014
snippet.description: Nikki Glaser, Nate Bargatze and Dan Soder make video games sexier, watch product reviews on YouTube and check on the medical status of Pierre the Pelican.

snippet.title: Tuesday, April 1, 2014
snippet.description: Kumail Nanjiani, Thomas Middleditch and T.J. Miller celebrate April Fools' Day with David Hasselhoff, list #FailedApps and tweet as a redneck possum.
